Module Robotinterface
Package robotinterface.debug

Interface Out

All Known Implementing Classes:
SimDebugOut
public interface Out
A line-based text output to print texts to a console. Using this class, text lines not only appear at the command line console, but can also be presented on a screen in the simulation environment. In addition, remote debugging is supported, i.e. the real robot can pass its texts via network to the simulation environment.
Author:
Jörg Roth (Joerg.Roth@Wireless-earth.org)
